com.alexgilleran.icesoap.parser

Interface ItemObserver<TypeToReturn>

  • Type Parameters:
    TypeToReturn - The type of object that will be returned by the parser.

    public interface ItemObserver<TypeToReturn>
    Defines classes that can be set up to receive new item events from an IceSoapListParser.
    Author:
    Alex Gilleran

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onNewItem(TypeToReturn item)
      This is called every time a new item is completely parsed.

    • Method Detail

      • onNewItem

        void onNewItem(TypeToReturn item)
        This is called every time a new item is completely parsed. Note that this will not be called for null (xsi:nil) items.
        Parameters:
        item - The newly parsed item.
